data.description: First time buyer? Investor? Rare opportunity to enjoy the explosive growth of Leland and all it has to offer from shopping and restaurants to business and more - from the secluded hideaway of Fletcher Estates, an established, cozy 21-home community located just minutes from Hwy 74/76 and I-140 for easy access to Wilmington, Myrtle Beach and beyond! With 3 bedrooms & 2 baths and vaulted ceilings, the spacious floor plan and large private backyard offers plenty of room for growth. Beautifully maintained hardwood floors extend from the living room through the kitchen. A sizable utility room off the 2 car garage can be used for office, storage or workshop. Listed under $300k - it won't last long!!
